pts/08-repo-quality-tooling.summary.md:147:1. I briefly introduced a mistake in the root `Makefile` where `make test` also called frontend lint. I caught that during inspection and removed it before final verification.\nfrontend/src/shared/ui/buttonStyles.ts:12:  tone?: ButtonTone\nfrontend/src/shared/ui/buttonStyles.ts:19:  tone = 'primary',\nfrontend/src/shared/ui/buttonStyles.ts:23:    `button--${tone}`,\nfrontend/src/shared/ui/workflow.test.tsx:20:        error=\"A tone is required.\"\ndocs/domain-model.md:9:- Every workflow stage is tracked explicitly, even when later stages are generated from earlier ones.\ndocs/domain-model.md:26:| `selected_genre_id` | Accepted genre catalog row for the session. |\ndocs/domain-model.md:27:| `selected_tone_profile_id` | Accepted tone profile row for the session. |\ndocs/domain-model.md:50:| `workflow_stage_state` | Per-stage state for the session. | `session_id`, `stage`, `status`, `updated_at`, `last_event_id`. | Stored explicitly so resume does not depend on sparse child tables. |\ndocs/domain-model.md:51:| `genre` | Curated genre catalog entry. | slug, label, description, bedtime-safety notes, arc notes. | Backend-owned reference data. |\ndocs/domain-model.md:52:| `tone_profile` | Curated tone option linked to a genre. | `genre_id`, slug, label, descriptors, bedtime notes, default planning hints. | Tone choices are filtered by genre. |\ndocs/domain-model.md:53:| `story_brief` | User-authored idea plus any normalized planning summary. | raw brief text, normalized summary, revision number. | Keeps user input separate from later generated planning outputs. |\ndocs/domain-model.md:70:| 1 | `genre` | Genre | The user accepts a genre for the session. |\ndocs/domain-model.md:71:| 2 | `tone` | Tone | The user accepts a tone profile for the selected genre. |\ndocs/domain-model.md:72:| 3 | `brief` | Story brief | The session has an accepted free-form brief and any required normalized summary. |\ndocs/domain-model.md:94:| `draft` | The stage has no accepted durable output yet. Partial input may exist, but the stage is not considered complete. | The user typed part of a brief but has not accepted it yet. |\ndocs/domain-model.md:112:`genre -> tone -> brief -> pitches -> characters -> beats -> story_setup -> composition -> audio -> finalize`\ndocs/domain-model.md:131:| `genre` | `tone`, `brief`, `pitches`, `characters`, `beats`, `composition`, `audio`, `finalize` |\ndocs/domain-model.md:132:| `tone` | `brief`, `pitches`, `characters`, `beats`, `composition`, `audio`, `finalize` |\ndocs/domain-model.md:133:| `brief` | `pitches`, `characters`, `beats`, `composition`, `audio`, `finalize` |\ndocs/domain-model.md:163:   - Example: `genre`, `tone`, and `brief` are `completed`; `pitches` is `in_progress`.\ndocs/frontend-design-foundation.md:13:- Color: bedtime-friendly ink, surface, brand, moss, gold, and rose tones are\ndocs/frontend-design-foundation.md:60:  <Badge tone=\"brand\">Draft</Badge>\nbackend/app/services/session_hydration.py:33:    get_workflow_stage_definition,\nbackend/app/services/session_hydration.py:153:        selected_genre=build_catalog_selection(story_session.selected_genre),\nbackend/app/services/session_hydration.py:154:        selected_tone_profile=build_catalog_selection(story_session.selected_tone_profile),\nbackend/app/services/session_hydration.py:155:        progress=build_progress(story_session.workflow_stage_states),\nbackend/app/services/session_hydration.py:171:                aggregate.active_story_brief.normalized_summary\nbackend/app/services/session_hydration.py:172:                if aggregate.active_story_brief\nbackend/app/services/session_hydration.py:175:            raw_brief=(\nbackend/app/services/session_hydration.py:176:                aggregate.active_story_brief.raw_brief if aggregate.active_story_brief else None\nbackend/app/services/session_hydration.py:187:        selected_genre=build_catalog_selection(story_session.selected_genre),\nbackend/app/service