l\": 100}, \"timestap\": \"2026-03-31T22:50:33-07:00\"}\nprompts/11-postgres-schema-and-migrations.yolopilot.jsonlines:155:{\"color\": \"cyan\", \"emoji\": \"\\ud83d\\udee0\\ufe0f\", \"event_type\": \"Command Finished\", \"message\": \"completed, exit 0: /bin/zsh -lc \\\"./scripts/dev-compose.sh exec -T postgres psql -U storyteller -d storyteller_prompt11 -c \\\\\\\"SELECT tablename FROM pg_tables WHERE schemaname = 'public' ORDER BY tablename;\\\\\\\"\\\"\", \"raw_event\": {\"item\": {\"aggregated_output\": \"       tablename       \\n-----------------------\\n alembic_version\\n audio_jobs\\n beat_sheets\\n character_sheets\\n composition_jobs\\n composition_segments\\n event_log_entries\\n export_assets\\n genres\\n pitches\\n story_briefs\\n story_sessions\\n story_setups\\n tone_profiles\\n workflow_stage_states\\n(15 rows)\\n\\n\", \"command\": \"/bin/zsh -lc \\\"./scripts/dev-compose.sh exec -T postgres psql -U storyteller -d storyteller_prompt11 -c \\\\\\\"SELECT tablename FROM pg_tables WHERE schemaname = 'public' ORDER BY tablename;\\\\\\\"\\\"\", \"exit_code\": 0, \"id\": \"item_81\", \"status\": \"completed\", \"type\": \"command_execution\"}, \"type\": \"item.completed\"}, \"task_display_context\": {\"event_number\": 155, \"prompt_index\": 12, \"prompt_name\": \"11 \\u2014 PostgreSQL Schema and Database Migrations\", \"prompt_total\": 100}, \"timestap\": \"2026-03-31T22:53:10-07:00\"}\nprompts/11-postgres-schema-and-migrations.yolopilot.jsonlines:175:{\"color\": \"green\", \"emoji\": \"\\ud83d\\udcac\", \"event_type\": \"Agent Message\", \"message\": \"Implemented the first real SQLAlchemy/Alembic persistence layer for the backend: explicit ORM models for sessions, workflow stage state, briefs, pitches, character sheets, beat sheets, story setup, composition/audio jobs, composition seg...\", \"raw_event\": {\"item\": {\"id\": \"item_92\", \"text\": \"Implemented the first real SQLAlchemy/Alembic persistence layer for the backend: explicit ORM models for sessions, workflow stage state, briefs, pitches, character sheets, beat sheets, story setup, composition/audio jobs, composition segments, export assets, and the event log, plus the initial migration at [20260331_01_initial_storyteller_schema.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/migrations/versions/20260331_01_initial_storyteller_schema.py). I also added shared DB base/session helpers, migration docs in [backend/README.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/README.md) and [backend/migrations/README.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/migrations/README.md), and updated the architecture/domain docs to reflect the first-schema tradeoff of tracking accepted child rows on the child tables to avoid circular foreign keys.\\n\\nVerification passed end to end: `make check`, focused backend tests, SQLite Alembic cycle tests, and a live PostgreSQL `alembic upgrade head -> downgrade base -> upgrade head` run against the compose `postgres` service. No browser checks were needed because this prompt only changed backend persistence. The required reviewer summary is written at [11-postgres-schema-and-migrations.summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/prompts/11-postgres-schema-and-migrations.summary.md). Checkpoint commits: `16b904e` and `89ad342`.\", \"type\": \"agent_message\"}, \"type\": \"item.completed\"}, \"task_display_context\": {\"event_number\": 175, \"prompt_index\": 12, \"prompt_name\": \"11 \\u2014 PostgreSQL Schema and Database Migrations\", \"prompt_total\": 100}, \"timestap\": \"2026-03-31T22:55:18-07:00\"}\nbackend/tests/test_action_policy_service.py:56:def test_policy_rejects_tone_selection_without_genre_and_suggests_prerequisite(\nbackend/tests/test_action_policy_service.py:68:                        \"action_type\": \"select_tone\",\nbackend/tests/test_action_policy_service.py:69:                        \"target_stage\": \"tone\",\nbackend/tests/test_action_policy_service.py:71:                        \"rationale\": \"The user explicitly named a