{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I\u2019ve confirmed the backend checkpoint is isolated and the remaining gap is entirely on the frontend: wiring the dedicated brief stage cleanly, styling its preview state, and updating the workspace tests around save and chat-driven brief...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_159", "text": "I\u2019ve confirmed the backend checkpoint is isolated and the remaining gap is entirely on the frontend: wiring the dedicated brief stage cleanly, styling its preview state, and updating the workspace tests around save and chat-driven brief edits. Next I\u2019m tightening those files and then I\u2019ll run the targeted frontend suite before browser QA.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 303, "prompt_index": 43, "prompt_name": "42 \u2014 Story Setup Brief Form", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T19:45:36-07:00"}
