{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The live database behind the compose-connected backend was one migration behind. The new `story_brief` fields were already in code, but the running DB didn\u2019t have those columns yet, which is why session creation was throwing `UndefinedCo...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_244", "text": "The live database behind the compose-connected backend was one migration behind. The new `story_brief` fields were already in code, but the running DB didn\u2019t have those columns yet, which is why session creation was throwing `UndefinedColumn`. I\u2019m upgrading the live DB to `head` now so the browser QA run matches the code I just verified in tests.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 461, "prompt_index": 43, "prompt_name": "42 \u2014 Story Setup Brief Form", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T19:55:35-07:00"}
