{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented prompt 42 end to end. The backend now persists structured story brief fields through [sessions.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/services/sessions.py) and [sessions.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/ap...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_325", "text": "Implemented prompt 42 end to end. The backend now persists structured story brief fields through [sessions.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/services/sessions.py) and [sessions.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/api/v1/routes/sessions.py), and the frontend now mounts a dedicated [StoryBriefStage.tsx](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/features/session/StoryBriefStage.tsx) wired through [SessionWorkspacePage.tsx](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/pages/session/SessionWorkspacePage.tsx). The stage supports a required free-form story idea, optional specificity cues, a composed planner preview, save/reset behavior, resume/edit hydration, and accepted chat-driven `update_story_brief` auto-apply.\n\nVerification passed:\n- `npm --prefix frontend test`: `58 passed`\n- `npm --prefix frontend run lint` and `npm --prefix frontend run build`: passed\n- `cd backend && .venv/bin/python -m pytest tests/test_session_service.py tests/test_session_api.py tests/test_db_models.py tests/test_migrations.py tests/integration/test_data_layer.py -q`: `43 passed, 5 skipped`\n- `cd backend && .venv/bin/python -m ruff check app tests`: passed\n- Browser QA against the live app: [prompt-42-story-brief-desktop.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-42-story-brief-desktop.png), [prompt-42-story-brief-mobile-stage.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-42-story-brief-mobile-stage.png), [prompt-42-story-brief-after-save-stage.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-42-story-brief-after-save-stage.png)\n\nI also upgraded the live dev DB to migration `20260401_03` during browser QA because the running backend container was one migration behind and `story_briefs.story_idea` was missing. Code checkpoints are `0c7d6f3` and `c074b62`. The required reviewer summary is written at [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/42_story_setup_brief_form/summary.md).", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 612, "prompt_index": 43, "prompt_name": "42 \u2014 Story Setup Brief Form", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T20:10:42-07:00"}
